</li></ul><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-556_">Cultivate a culture of safety
</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-558_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Creating a culture prioritising safety requires leadership commitment, transparency in reporting errors, and a non-punitive approach to incident reporting. Encouraging open communication and learning from mistakes are essential for fostering a supportive environment where risks are actively managed.
