</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-562_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Regular and systematic risk assessments can identify potential hazards before they result in harm. Tools such as Failure Mode and Effects Analysis (FMEA) and root cause analysis can provide insights into underlying issues, enabling proactive measures to mitigate risks.
